# Source ALL files ending in .zsh ANYWHERE under the compoenents directory.
#   So you could, for example, add another set of config files by just throwing
#   them into a directory within your own components directory.
#
#   This file is provided as a shorter alternative to the default zshrc.
#   Honestly, I'm not sure why.
source =(cat $HOME/.zsh/include/**/*.zsh)
